            → Empezar el quiz
          </a>
          <a
            href="/botas"
            class="inline-block px-8 py-5 border-2 border-zinc-600 text-zinc-300 hover:border-lime-500 hover:text-lime-400 font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-lg transition-all"
